description: Bobby Zankel and the Warriors of the Wonderful Sound are embarking on a new project with famed composer Muhal Richard Abrams, to premiere April 28, 2012 at Montgomery County Community College. Here, Vijay Iyer shares some of his thoughts on Muhal.
